content:
Customize the Incident Alerts All Tab

You can add only public or shared list views to the Incident Alerts All tab. Create a custom Incidents list view.
From Setup, enter Customer Service Incident Management and click Customer Service Incident Management.
Find Add Incident Alerts Utility and select Go to App Manager.
Click Edit on the console app that uses the Incident Alerts utility.
Select Incident Alerts under Utility Items.
Under Component Properties, find All Incidents List View, and select your custom public or shared list view.
Save your changes. Refresh the browser to see the new list view from the Incident Alerts utility.
title: Customizing Incident Alerts in Service Cloud
